      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>A <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">revetment</rs> <rs type="objectType">panel</rs>, re-used in the flooring of the
baths.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>In its present position the inscription is difficult to
see, and l.6 is truncated.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Irregular, careful and very ornate: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.035-0.05</measure>.</p>
      </div>

